	$LF
]div
[h4 id=44 
	" 4-4
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"grab the meat then get past the  guards.
	$LF
	"Some swimming technique here is to jump and flip whenever possible, as it makes us go 512 speed, as soon as we go to normal bonk, just let go of the d-pad to keep speed.
	$LF
]div
