	" 5-3
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Hardest stage for RTA runners.  Most of the enemies like the fish spawn when you’re at a certain position, we can manipulate it so we trigger them to be as high as possible.  The sword bat enemies also will move if you’re slightly above it in y position.  
	$LF
	"Right at the end we can get two flies to jump off of and take damage to hit the end trigger faster
	$LF
]div
